** imp - run tmux -u for full utf support (in case if dev-icons are not working )
 
=========tmux basics ============
-- remapped -- see tmux.conf for more details
prefix - <C-a>

1. Sessions
----------------

a. tmux ls  - list sessions
b. tmux attach -t {session #}
c. prefix -d    - deattach current session
d. tmux     - new session
e. tmux new -s {session name}
f. prefix :rename-session    - rename session from inside tmux
g. prefix -s    - shows windows in a session(navigate and select)

-----
kill-session
a. prefix :kill-session     - kill session from within
b. tmux kill-session -t {session name/#}
c. tmux kill-server     - kill all sessions
d. :kill-window -t [window_number] 


2. panes and windows
-----------------
a. vertical and horizontal spilt
prefix-v
prefix- -

b. prefix-c     -new window

c. navigating windows and panes
prefix-p
prefix-n
prefix-{number}

prefix-h/j/k/l  - select pane

* note - for navigating windows - prefix-<C-h> or prefix-<C-l>, also works ,but numbers/p/n are more comfortable
d. resizing panes
prefix-H/J/K/L
prefix-z     - toggle current pane fullscreen

e. prefix ,      - rename current window

